				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Looks like your nes is working completely fine.<br /><br />The blue bar on the left is just an option games can turn on to blank the left side.<br />The blue color bleed is probably just your tv not handeling the nes' video very well.<br /><br />Lcds in general tend to not interpret nes video very well. In particular they tend to interpret the 240p signal as 480i, which can explain some of the ugliness when things start moving.<br />Note that the nes video out is always a bit jaggy though even on a crt.</div>

