					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Colour bleed like that with the NES is normal, I think. I don't know how much your camera and/or TV is emphasizing it but it is inherent in the signal. Example demonstration: <a href="https://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=15080" class="postlink">https://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=15080</a><br /><br />The bar on the left side of the screen is also a very normal thing, done intentionally by the game. Super Mario 3 will do it too, and countless others.</div>

